{
  "chapter": 213,
  "chapter_summary": "第213章讲述项少龙在醉风楼宴会上揭破伍孚暗中为吕不韦办事的阴谋，伍孚心虚跪地。嫪毐因伍孚欺瞒单美美去陪吕不韦一事而愤怒。蒲鶮趁机观察众人反应。石素芳以声色艺三绝惊艳登场，唱《采薇》名动四方。金老大出场，受蒲鶮指使挑拨嫪毐对项少龙的妒忌。吕不韦携管中邪、许商突然现身，以三杯罚酒公然打压嫪毐，矛盾彻底表面化。项少龙识破吕不韦反间之计，出面化解第三杯罚酒的尴尬，吕不韦公开纳单美美为侍妾，嫪毐忍气吞声，双方冲突已不可调和。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_wu_fu",
      "text": "伍楼主不是做了什么错事吧？所谓'平生不做亏心事，夜半敲门心不惊'。楼主看来却刚刚相反，听了区区一句话立即跪了下来，所为何事呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 213,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_fu",
      "speaker_name": "伍孚",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "小人只是一时失足，闪得跪跌下来，教各位大人爷们见笑了。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 213,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ai",
      "speaker_name": "嫪毐",
      "listener": "char_wu_fu",
      "text": "楼主来此，不是有如项大人所言，要把美美送与仲父吧？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 213,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_fu",
      "speaker_name": "伍孚",
      "listener": "char_lao_ai",
      "text": "实情确是如此，不过若内史大人不高兴，小人这就回去推掉仲父好了。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 213,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_mei_mei",
      "speaker_name": "单美美",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项大将军刚才出去打了一个转，是否恰巧碰到仲父？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 213,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我没有见到仲父，但我的手下却见到他的随从，所以随口一猜，怎知却害得伍楼主摔了一跤。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 213,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ai",
      "speaker_name": "嫪毐",
      "listener": "char_wu_fu",
      "text": "楼主该知眼下应怎么做吧？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 213,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pu_he",
      "speaker_name": "蒲鶮",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "'平生不做亏心事，夜半敲门心不惊'，这极有意思的句语我蒲鶮尚是初次得闻，项大人妙语连珠，蒲鶮敬你一杯。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 213,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ai",
      "speaker_name": "嫪毐",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不若让我们暂忘明天将要发生的事，先欣赏三大名姬之一的石素芳声、色、艺三绝的精彩演出吧！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 213,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今朝有酒今朝醉，明日愁来明日当，我们再喝一杯。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 213,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_cheng_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "金成就",
      "listener": "char_pu_he",
      "text": "金成就参见蒲爷和各位大人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 213,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pu_he",
      "speaker_name": "蒲鶮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这位是金老大，全赖他的苦心训练，各位得以听到刚才比仙籁还动人的歌声。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 213,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ai",
      "speaker_name": "嫪毐",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "人来，给我赏金老大十镒黄金。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 213,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pu_he",
      "speaker_name": "蒲鶮",
      "listener": "char_jin_cheng_jiu",
      "text": "石姑娘今晚心情如何？可否请她来陪我们闲聊两句，好让我等表达仰慕之情。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 213,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_cheng_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "金成就",
      "listener": "char_pu_he",
      "text": "我这女儿绝不能对她操之过急。待小人找到时机，再安排她和诸位大人见面，此事可包在小人身上。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 213,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_cheng_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "金成就",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我这女儿一向眼高于顶，但对项大人却特别留心。今晚因知道大人有份出席，特别开心，还唱出她的首本名曲。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 213,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ai",
      "speaker_name": "嫪毐",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既是如此，金老大只须安排石小姐和项大人私下相见就可以，有我们这些旁人在，反为碍事。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 213,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_lao_ai",
      "text": "嫪大人切勿对金老大的话认真，我看石小姐对任何人都不在意才是真的。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 213,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": "char_lao_ai",
      "text": "我今趟来是要罚内史大人三杯酒。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 213,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ai",
      "speaker_name": "嫪毐",
      "listener": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "text": "仲父为何要对卑职兴问罪之师呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 213,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "少龙、蒲老板和诸位美人儿可做见证，让我逐项罪一一数出来，看是否罚得有理。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 213,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_shang",
      "speaker_name": "许商",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还不给内史大人先斟第一杯罚酒？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 213,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "美人们请坐！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 213,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": "char_lao_ai",
      "text": "首项罪名，是明知本仲父来了醉风楼，竟不过来打个招呼，何时我们的关系变得和陌路人没有任何分别？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 213,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ai",
      "speaker_name": "嫪毐",
      "listener": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "text": "该罚！该罚！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 213,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pu_he",
      "speaker_name": "蒲鶮",
      "listener": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "text": "仲父第一杯罚酒，罚的该是我们全体才对。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 213,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": "char_pu_he",
      "text": "本仲父怎敢怪蒲老板，但责怪小嫪却是理所当然，是吗？内史大人？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 213,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ai",
      "speaker_name": "嫪毐",
      "listener": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "text": "仲父的话自然错不了，只不知第二杯罚的是什么？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 213,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙料事如神，不若由你来猜猜看。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 213,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "text": "仲父行事出人意表，教我如何猜测？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 213,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": "char_lao_ai",
      "text": "第二杯仍是与第一杯罚的事有关，刚才碰上金老大，问起来始知小嫪私下安排在此欣赏三绝女的声、色、艺，如此难逢的机会，小嫪怎可漏了我吕不韦的一份儿？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 213,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guan_zhong_xie",
      "speaker_name": "管中邪",
      "listener": "char_lao_ai",
      "text": "我当然没有资格责罚小嫪，却忍不住要怪小嫪不够朋友。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 213,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ai",
      "speaker_name": "嫪毐",
      "listener": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "text": "第三杯罚酒，恕卑职真的想不到原因。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 213,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "text": "若第三项罪名是与美美小姐有关，可否请仲父暂时放过内史大人，不再说出来，那就皆大欢喜，大家可以各自快乐地回家睡觉。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 213,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "还是少龙了得，就因你这几句话，本仲父收回第三杯罚酒。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 213,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": "char_shan_mei_mei",
      "text": "美美你先回小楼，转头本仲父来见你。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 213,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ai",
      "speaker_name": "嫪毐",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "夜了！大家早点休息也好。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 213,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ai",
      "speaker_name": "嫪毐",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在我只想到外面吸两口清新的空气。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 213,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 306
    }
  ],
